---
By: David Hawkins
Source:
  ISBN: 978-1571746931
  Locus:
    Page: 260
  Title: The Essential Mystics, Poets, Saints and Sages
---
When one sees all things in their totality,
he recognizes that all things are perfect as they are,
and nothing from the outside is needed to change anything.
The limited ego thinks the world is in need of fixing,
but this is an illusion and vanity.
